{"title":"SR Suntour shows prototype electronic suspension on Tom Pidcock’s Gold Medal MTB","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/02/sr-suntour-shows-prototype-electronic-suspension-on-tom-pidcocks-gold-medal-mtb/","date":1630583697000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270195\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Tom Pidcock’s Olympic winning XC race bike had a couple prototype parts on its mixed-brand build, but the most secretive was the electronically controlled SR Suntour fork and shock. What makes it so interesting is the complete lack of visible controls, power source, or even sensors to pickup movement at the axle…</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:740x555/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"tom pidcock's olympic gold medal winning xc mountain bike with prototype SR Suntour electronic suspension shown at eurobike 2021\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1350\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-800x600.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-120x90.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-768x576.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-1536x1152.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:740x555/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.3939326616851706\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-800x600.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-120x90.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-768x576.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070625/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-2-1536x1152.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1536w\"></a></p><p>Top level, the bike is a BMC FourStroke stripped of its branding. Pidcock is sponsored by Pinarello, but without a current mountain bike, he needed something to ride. This gave him the freedom to build it up with some exceptionally light parts from an assortment of brands, but the base is the 100mm travel full suspension <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/09/07/all-new-bmc-fourstroke-01-gets-rad-with-integrated-80mm-oval-xc-dropper-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FourStroke 01 launched in 2018</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070659/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-11-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12.jpg\" alt=\"bmc fourstroke 01 mountain bike with integrated 80mm dropper seatpost\" width=\"1825\" height=\"675\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12.jpg 1825w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-1536x568.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1825px) 100vw, 1825px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12.jpg 1825w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070712/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-12-1536x568.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>What makes this bike unique is its integrated dropper seatpost, offering 80mm of travel without the usual stanchion in a post design. Instead, an ovalized seat tube slides up and down directly through a seal at the seat tube’s opening, where the collar normally goes. It clamps into position to set saddle height further down inside the seat tube. Check <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/09/07/all-new-bmc-fourstroke-01-gets-rad-with-integrated-80mm-oval-xc-dropper-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our story about this bike</a> to see how it works in more detail.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of prototype electronically controlled suspension on tom pidcock's olympic mountain bike\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070637/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>SR Suntour outfitted it with an unmarked rear shock that had a small electronics box attached to it.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of prototype electronically controlled suspension on tom pidcock's olympic mountain bike\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070641/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-5-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>From the looks of the air can’s shape, it’s their Edge Plus inline rear shock, which has a slightly larger air volume than the standard Edge shocks. The electronics box sits where the compression damping controls would be, suggesting it’s adjusting compression damping for the rider. The red rebound knob keeps that setting external, and manual.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of prototype electronically controlled suspension on tom pidcock's olympic mountain bike\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070648/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-8-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Up front, a single wire leads to the top of the fork, again where compression damping controls usually go. The cap is fixed, there’s no adjustment (even though that tab looks like it would be used to turn the dial), so it’s relying entirely on the internal electronics to control the damping.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070722/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-14.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070722/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-14.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of prototype electronically controlled suspension on tom pidcock's olympic mountain bike\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070722/sr-suntour-tom-pidcock-olympic-gold-medal-mountain-bike-details-14.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02070722/sr-